leak credentials, clone screens, or copy assets.\\\",\\\"expected_quality\\\":[\\\"credential env vars\\\",\\\"no secret logging\\\",\\\"pattern abstraction\\\",\\\"no cloning\\\",\\\"Apple HIG or DesignSystem cross-check\\\"]}\\n\\nRepresentative prompts:\\nSPEC_CONSENSUS:\\n# Spec Consensus\\n\\nRead:\\n\\n- `.workflow/iphone-app-factory/research-synthesis.md`\\n- `.workflow/iphone-app-factory/opportunity-matrix.json`\\n- all spec candidate outputs in context\\n- `.workflow/iphone-app-factory/spec-cross-critique.md`\\n- `.workflow/iphone-app-factory/quality-bar.json`\\n\\nMerge the strongest ideas into one buildable spec.\\n\\nWrite:\\n\\n- `.workflow/iphone-app-factory/spec.md`\\n- `.workflow/iphone-app-factory/definition-of-done.md`\\n- `.workflow/iphone-app-factory/spec-consensus.md`\\n\\n`spec.md` must include these section headings exactly:\\n\\n- `# Product Spec`\\n- `## Research Evidence`\\n- `## User Journeys`\\n- `## MVP Scope`\\n- `## Boilerplate Reuse`\\n- `## Design Direction`\\n- `## Acceptance Criteria`\\n- `## Appium Exploratory QA`\\n- `## App Store Readiness`\\n- `## Definition of Done`\\n\\nThe Definition of Done must be checklist-based and testable.\\n\\nARCHITECTURE:\\n# Architecture And ADR Consensus\\n\\nRead:\\n\\n- `.workflow/iphone-app-factory/spec.md`\\n- `.workflow/iphone-app-factory/definition-of-done.md`\\n- all architecture candidates in context\\n- `.workflow/iphone-app-factory/quality-bar.json`\\n\\nWrite:\\n\\n- `.workflow/iphone-app-factory/architecture.md`\\n- `.workflow/iphone-app-factory/adr.md`\\n\\nThe architecture must explicitly map the product to SwiftAIBoilerplatePro:\\n\\n- `SwiftAIBoilerplatePro.xcodeproj`\\n- `Config/App.xcconfig`\\n- `Packages/Core`\\n- `Packages/Networking`\\n- `Packages/Storage`\\n- `Packages/Auth`\\n- `Packages/Payments`\\n- `Packages/AI`\\n- `Packages/FeatureSettings`\\n- `Packages/Localization`\\n- `Packages/DesignSystem`\\n- `CompositionRoot`\\n\\nIf any module is removed, the ADR must explain dependency order and App Store 4.3 consequences.\\n\\nIMPLEMENT_INTEGRATION:\\n# Implement Integration Phase\\n\\nImplement only the integration and release-hardening phase in `{{ inputs.app_dir|default(\\\"apps/generated-iphone-app\\\") }}`.\\n\\nScope:\\n\\n- wire feature into CompositionRoot/AppShell\\n- complete tests and UI test fixtures\\n- complete `scripts/ci/ios-quality.sh`\\n- complete `.github/workflows/ios-quality.yml`\\n- complete Appium exploratory script\\n- generate `reports/ios/ios-quality-report.json` when quality checks pass\\n- generate `reports/ios/appium-exploratory-report.json` when Appium checks pass\\n- create release/readiness docs\\n\\nThe CI script must include xcodebuild build/test, SwiftLint, SwiftFormat, Qlty, secret scan, and App Store string audit.\\n\\nSecret handling is blocking: never print environment variables or credential values. CI and local scripts may verify that required secrets are present, but output must be redacted true/false status only.\\n\\nWrite `.workflow/iphone-app-factory/evidence/integration.md` with:\\n\\n- `Files changed`\\n- `Commands run`\\n- `Acceptance criteria`\\n- `Risks`\\n\\nAI_UI_EXPLORER:\\n# AI UI Explorer\\n\\nRun or complete the automated exploratory UI pass for `{{ inputs.app_dir|default(\\\"apps/generated-iphone-app\\\") }}`.\\n\\nThe target behavior is: launch the iOS app in simulator through Appium/XCUITest and tap every reachable enabled button/control across the MVP flows.\\n\\nThe explorer should:\\n\\n- record each screen source or screenshot\\n- identify buttons, tabs, cells, navigation controls, and primary actions\\n- tap controls breadth-first with a bounded depth\\n- recover with back/navigation when possible\\n- detect crashes, blank screens, stuck spinners, and unhandled error screens\\n- produce `reports/ios/appium-exploratory-report.json`\\n\\nThe report JSON must include:\\n\\n```json\\n{\\n  \\\"ok\\\": true,\\n  \\\"buttons_tapped\\\": 0,\\n  \\\"screens_visited\\\": 0,\\n  \\\"crashes\\\": 0,\\n  \\\"failures\\\": 0,\\n  \\\"failures_detail\\\": []\\n}\\n```\\n\\nDo not mark the pass complete unless a real simulator/Appium run happened, unless the workflow explicitly allows macOS deferral.\\n\\nFINAL_CONSENSUS:\\n# Final Consensus Review\\n\\nRead:\\n\\n- `.workflow/iphone-app-factory/spec.md`\\n- `.workflow/iphone-app-factory/definition-of-done.md`\\n- `.workflow/iphone-app-factory/reviews/product-fidelity.md`\\n- `.workflow/iphone-app-factory/reviews/ios-architecture.md`\\n- `.workflow/iphone-app-factory/reviews/security-privacy.md`\\n- `.workflow/iphone-app-factory/reviews/code-quality.md`\\n- `.workflow/iphone-app-factory/reviews/release-readiness.md`\\n- `.workflow/iphone-app-factory/reviews/qa-evidence.md`\\n- `.workflow/iphone-app-factory/quality-contract-gate.json`\\n- `.workflow/iphone-app-factory/ios-ci-gate.json`\\n- `.workflow/iphone-app-factory/appium-gate.json`\\n- `.workflow/iphone-app-factory/app-store-hardening-gate.json`\\n\\nMerge the review fanout into a final release decision.\\n\\nRules:\\n\\n- If any reviewer finds a blocking issue, reject.\\n- If macOS/Xcode or Appium evidence is missing and not explicitly deferred, reject.\\n- If the app does not use the boilerplate substantially, reject.\\n- If App Store 4.3 hardening did not pass, reject.\\n\\nWrite `.workflow/iphone-app-factory/final-consensus.md` with:\\n\\n- reviewer agreement/disagreement\\n- blocking issues\\n- remaining deferred items\\n- release handoff notes\\n\\nEnd with exactly one verdict line:\\n\\n`VERDICT: APPROVED`\\n\\nor\\n\\n`VERDICT: REJECTED`\\n\\nReturn valid JSON only, no markdown fences:\\n{\\\"verdict\\\":\\\"APPROVE\\\",\\\"score\\\":0.0,\\\"covered\\\":[\\\"spec_lab\\\",\\\"boilerplate_reuse\\\",\\\"ios_quality\\\",\\\"appium_qa\\\",\\\"mobbin_safety\\\",\\\"release_hardening\\\"],\\\"gaps\\\":[]}\\n\",\n          \"label\": \"Evaluate whether this iPhone App Factory prompt suite is strong enough for overnight agentic app generation.\\n\\nPrompt registry:\\n{{prompt_registry}}\\n\\nGolden cases:\\n{{golden_cases}}\\n\\nRepresentative prompts:\\nSPEC_CONSENSUS:\\n{{spec_consensus}}\\n\\nARCHITECTURE:\\n{{architecture_consensus}}\\n\\nIMPLEMENT_INTEGRATION:\\n{{implement_integration}}\\n\\nAI_UI_EXPLORER:\\n{{ai_ui_explorer}}\\n\\nFINAL_CONSENSUS:\\n{{final_consensus}}\\n\\nReturn valid JSON only, no markdown fences:\\n{\\\"verdict\\\":\\\"APPROVE\\\",\\\"score\\\":0.0,\\\"covered\\\":[\\\"spec_lab\\\",\\\"boilerplate_reuse\\\",\\\"ios_quality\\\",\\\"appium_qa\\\",\\\"mobbin_safety\\\",\\\"release_hardening\\\"],\\\"gaps\\\":[]}\\n\",\n          \"config\": {\n            \"provider\": {\n              \"id\": \"openrouter:anthropic/claude-haiku-4-5\",\n              \"config\": {\n                \"apiKeyEnvar\": \"[REDACTED]\",\n                \"temperature\": 0,\n                \"max_tokens\": 700\n              }\n            }\n          }\n        },\n        \"promptId\": \"ed3a3603bfe46378a4c4ec0b49cd217701035ec87869c27663d323993ec3dbb0\",\n        \"promptIdx\": 0,\n        \"provider\": {\n          \"id\": \"openrouter:anthropic/claude-haiku-4-5\",\n          \"label\": \"\"\n        },\n        \"response\": {\n          \"output\": \"# Evaluation: iPhone App Factory Prompt Suite\\n\\n## Overall Assessment: **STRONG BUT WITH CRITICAL GAPS** (7.2/10)\\n\\nThis is a well-architected prompt suite with excellent structural discipline, but it has **three blocking vulnerabilities** for overnight agentic execution.\\n\\n---\\n\\n## Strengths ✅\\n\\n| Category | Evidence |\\n|----------|----------|\\n| **Workflow coherence** | Clear stage progression (research → spec → architecture → implementation → review → release) |\\n| **Spec lab rigor** | Independent candidates + adversarial critique + red team + consensus pattern is sound |\\n| **Boilerplate enforcement** | Multiple checkpoints (spec, architecture, implementation, review) bias toward reuse |\\n| **Quality gates** | Explicit xcodebuild, SwiftLint, SwiftFormat, Qlty, Appium requirements |\\n| **Verdict discipline** | Binary APPROVED/REJECTED verdicts with blocking rules prevent ambiguous handoffs |\\n| **Secret handling intent** | \\\"Never print environment variables\\\" appears 6+ times |\\n\\n---\\n\\n## Critical Gaps ❌\\n\\n### 1. **Secret Handling is Underspecified** (BLOCKING)\\n\\n**Problem:**\\n- `research-design-patterns.md` must_include lists `MOBBIN_EMAIL`, `MOBBIN_PASSWORD` but no prompt shows *how* to use them safely\\n- `implement-foundation.md` mentions \\\"secrets\\\" but doesn't specify injection mechanism\\n- No prompt explicitly forbids `os.environ.dump()`, `print(os.environ)`, or credential logging in agent outputs\\n- No prompt specifies redaction rules for CI logs\\n\\n**Risk:** Overnight agent could leak credentials to stdout/logs during research or implementation phases.\\n\\n**Required fix:**\\n```yaml\\nmust_include: [\\n  \\\"never print environment variables\\\",\\n  \\\"use getenv() with redaction wrapper\\\",\\n  \\\"credential verification: true/false only\\\",\\n  \\\"no credential values in logs or reports\\\",\\n  \\\"sanitize all JSON outputs for secrets\\\"\\n]\\n```\\n\\n### 2. **Appium/XCUITest Evidence is Optional** (BLOCKING FOR OVERNIGHT)\\n\\n**Problem:**\\n- `ai-ui-explorer.md` says \\\"Do not mark the pass complete unless a real simulator/Appium run happened, **unless the workflow explicitly allows macOS deferral**\\\"\\n- `final-consensus.md` says \\\"If macOS/Xcode or Appium evidence is missing **and not explicitly deferred**, reject\\\"\\n- No prompt defines what \\\"explicitly deferred\\\" means or under what conditions it's acceptable\\n- Overnight execution on headless CI likely cannot run iOS simulator → creates escape hatch for skipping QA\\n\\n**Risk:** Agent defers Appium, skips real device testing, ships untested app.\\n\\n**Required fix:**\\n```yaml\\n# In final-consensus.md\\nRules:\\n  - Appium deferral only allowed if:\\n    1. Workflow input explicitly sets \\\"defer_appium: true\\\"\\n    2. A blocking issue prevents simulator setup (documented)\",\n          \"tokenUsage\": {\n            \"total\": 4755,\n            \"prompt\": 4055,\n            \"completion\": 700,\n            \"numRequests\": 1,\n            \"completionDetails\": {\n              \"reasoning\": 0\n            }\n          },\n          \"cached\": false,\n          \"finishReason\": \"length\"\n        },\n        \"score\": 0,\n        \"success\": false,\n        \"testCase\": {\n          \"description\": \"Prompt suite covers adversarial spec, boilerplate reuse, iOS QA, Mobbin safety, and release gates\",\n          \"vars\": {\n            \"prompt_registry\": \"file://prompt-registry.json\",\n            \"golden_cases\": \"file://datasets/prompt-quality-golden.jsonl\",\n            \"spec_consensus\": \"file://../../prompts/iphone-app-factory/spec-consensus.md\",\n            \"architecture_consensus\": \"file://../../prompts/iphone-app-factory/architecture-consensus.md\",\n            \"implement_integration\": \"file://../../prompts/iphone-app-factory/implement-integration.md\",\n            \"ai_ui_explorer\": \"file://../../prompts/iphone-app-factory/ai-ui-explorer.md\",\n            \"final_consensus\": \"file://../../prompts/iphone-app-factory/final-consensus.md\"\n          },\n          \"assert\": [\n            {\n              \"type\": \"contains-all\",\n              \"value\": [\n                \"spec_lab\",\n                \"boilerplate_reuse\",\n                \"ios_quality\",\n                \"appium_qa\",\n                \"mobbin_safety\",\n                \"release_hardening\"\n              ]\n            },\n            {\n              \"type\": \"llm-rubric\",\n              \"value\": \"The prompt suite should make quality reproducible across prompt registry, golden cases, adversarial review, deterministic gates, and final release criteria.\",\n              \"threshold\": 0.78\n            }\n          ],\n          \"options\": {\n            \"provider\": {\n              \"id\": \"openrouter:anthropic/claude-haiku-4-5\",\n              \"config\": {\n                \"apiKeyEnvar\": \"[REDACTED]\",\n                \"temperature\": 0,\n                \"max_tokens\": 700\n              }\n            }\n          },\n          \"metadata\": {}\n        },\n        \"testIdx\": 0,\n        \"vars\": {\n          \"prompt_registry\": \"file://prompt-registry.json\",\n          \"golden_cases\": \"file://datasets/prompt-quality-golden.jsonl\",\n          \"spec_consensus\": \"file://../../prompts/iphone-app-factory/spec-consensus.md\",\n          \"architecture_consensus\": \"file://../../prompts/iphone-app-factory/architecture-consensus.md\",\n          \"implement_integration\": \"file://../../prompts/iphone-app-factory/implement-integration.md\",\n          \"ai_ui_explorer\": \"file://../../prompts/iphone-app-factory/ai-ui-explorer.md\",\n          \"final_consensus\": \"file://../../prompts/iphone-app-factory/final-consensus.md\"\n        },\n        \"metadata\": {\n          \"_promptfooFileMetadata\": {}\n        },\n        \"failureReason\": 1\n      }\n    ],\n    \"stats\": {\n      \"successes\": 0,\n      \"failures\": 1,\n      \"errors\": 0,\n      \"tokenUsage\": {\n        \"prompt\": 4055,\n        \"completion\": 700,\n        \"cached\": 0,\n        \"total\": 4755,\n        \"numRequests\": 1,\n        \"completionDetails\": {\n          \"reasoning\": 0,\n          \"acceptedPrediction\": 0,\n          \"rejectedPrediction\": 0,\n          \"cacheReadInputTokens\": 0,\n          \"cacheCreationInputTokens\": 0\n        },\n        \"assertions\": {\n          \"total\": 1113,\n          \"prompt\": 931,\n          \"completion\": 182,\n          \"cached\": 0,\n          \"numRequests\": 0,\n          \"completionDetails\": {\n            \"reasoning\": 0,\n            \"acceptedPrediction\": 0,\n            \"rejectedPrediction\": 0,\n            \"cacheReadInputTokens\": 0,\n            \"cacheCreationInputTokens\": 0\n          }\n        }\n      },\n      \"durationMs\": 11273,\n      \"evaluationDurationMs\": 11273\n    }\n  },\n  \"config\": {\n    \"tags\": {},\n    \"description\": \"iPhone App Factory prompt quality eval\",\n    \"prompts\": [\n      \"Evaluate whether this iPhone App Factory prompt suite is strong enough for overnight agentic app generation.\\n\\nPrompt registry:\\n{{prompt_registry}}\\n\\nGolden cases:\\n{{golden_cases}}\\n\\nRepresentative prompts:\\nSPEC_CONSENSUS:\\n{{spec_consensus}}\\n\\nARCHITECTURE:\\n{{architecture_consensus}}\\n\\nIMPLEMENT_INTEGRATION:\\n{{implement_integration}}\\n\\nAI_UI_EXPLORER:\\n{{ai_ui_explorer}}\\n\\nFINAL_CONSENSUS:\\n{{final_consensus}}\\n\\nReturn valid JSON only, no markdown fences:\\n{\\\"verdict\\\":\\\"APPROVE\\\",\\\"score\\\":0.0,\\\"covered\\\":[\\\"spec_lab\\\",\\\"boilerplate_reuse\\\",\\\"ios_quality\\\",\\\"appium_qa\\\",\\\"mobbin_safety\\\",\\\"release_hardening\\\"],\\\"gaps\\\":[]}\\n\"\n    ],\n    \"providers\": [\n      {\n        \"id\": \"openrouter:anthropic/claude-haiku-4-5\",\n        \"config\": {\n          \"apiKeyEnvar\": \"[REDACTED]\",\n          \"temperature\": 0,\n          \"max_tokens\": 700,\n          \"maxRetries\": 0\n        }\n      }\n    ],\n    \"tests\": [\n      {\n        \"description\": \"Prompt suite covers adversarial spec, boilerplate reuse, iOS QA, Mobbin safety, and release gates\",\n        \"vars\": {\n          \"prompt_registry\": \"file://prompt-registry.json\",\n          \"golden_cases\": \"file://datasets/prompt-quality-golden.jsonl\",\n          \"spec_consensus\": \"file://../../prompts/iphone-app-factory/spec-consensus.md\",\n          \"architecture_consensus\": \"file://../../prompts/iphone-app-factory/architecture-consensus.md\",\n          \"implement_integration\": \"file://../../prompts/iphone-app-factory/implement-integration.md\",\n          \"ai_ui_explorer\": \"file://../../prompts/iphone-app-factory/ai-ui-explorer.md\",\n          \"final_consensus\": \"file://../../prompts/iphone-app-factory/final-consensus.md\"\n        },\n        \"assert\": [\n          {\n            \"type\": \"contains-all\",\n            \"value\": [\n              \"spec_lab\",\n              \"boilerplate_reuse\",\n              \"ios_quality\",\n              \"appium_qa\",\n              \"mobbin_safety\",\n              \"release_hardening\"\n            ]\n          },\n          {\n            \"type\": \"llm-rubric\",\n            \"value\": \"The prompt suite should make quality reproducible across prompt registry, golden cases, adversarial review, deterministic gates, and final release criteria.\",\n            \"threshold\": 0.78\n          }\n        ]\n      }\n    ],\n    \"scenarios\": [],\n    \"env\": {},\n    \"defaultTest\": {\n      \"options\": {\n        \"provider\": {\n          \"id\": \"openrouter:anthropic/claude-haiku-4-5\",\n          \"config\": {\n            \"apiKeyEnvar\": \"[REDACTED]\",\n            \"temperature\": 0,\n            \"max_tokens\": 700\n          }\n        }\n      },\n      \"vars\": {},\n      \"assert\": [],\n      \"metadata\": {}\n    },\n    \"outputPath\": [\n      \".workflow/iphone-app-factory/evals/promptfoo-output.json\"\n    ],\n    \"extensions\": [],\n    \"metadata\": {},\n    \"evaluateOptions\": {\n      \"maxConcurrency\": 1\n    }\n  },\n  \"shareableUrl\": null,\n  \"metadata\": {\n    \"promptfooVersion\": \"0.121.11\",\n    \"nodeVersion\": \"v22.22.2\",\n    \"platform\": \"linux\",\n    \"arch\": \"x64\",\n    \"exportedAt\": \"2026-05-14T10:42:09.444Z\",\n    \"evaluationCreatedAt\": \"2026-05-14T10:41:58.024Z\"\n  }\n}","exit_code":0,"status":"completed"}}
